data.description: Lovely 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with 540 sq foot frog in Bray View Landing a water access sub-division. This home has a foyer, large living room with gas log fireplace, formal dining room, kitchen with breakfast area, large utility room, 2nd floor finished room with storage, front porch, closed in back porch, master bath with double sinks, jetted tub and shower, 2 car side garage, fenced in back yard with privacy fence, central heat and air including dual zone units, 1 year old electric water heater, new paint through out house, kitchen appliances convey, and .62 acre lot.  $40 yearly HOA fee which includes use of private neighborhood only boat ramp.
data.whatILove: quiet neighborhood, lots of space inside, huge fenced in backyard
